title: Pixel 4a Manual
content: PIXEL 4a NOT Pixel 4. Ordered. This will be my first new phone in 7 years. I have no idea what a new Android phone OS is like and what it can do now a days. My current phone is running Android "KitKat". Can anyone kindly provide me with the links that I should be checking prior to the phones arrival to see where I can download the manual for the 4a so I can get a head start. TIA.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 4
